            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "If you talk about this school, its very different from others like the best family environment, caring teachers and the best part is safety of your child. Not only this, kids here hold Guinness and Limca book of records in various fields. I also heard that its world's 1st school where kids created world's tallest santa claus and largest human santa hat. They also adopt very innovative teaching methods based on experiential learning that make kid creative and independent.  Parents, do visit the sector-38 branch once and feel the difference if you really care for your chiid. Last but not the least i am a very happy parent. Thank you Alpine Convent School.",
